The Secretary of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources (DENR) is hereby authorized to issue the corresponding Special Patent in favor of the Provincial Government of Abra.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila this 2 nd day of March, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Nine.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President:

Executive Secretary
